<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-11-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-11-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="314" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d314">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/7501</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the French Ambassador</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_JJJ2" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Jusserand</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">No. 1984</seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-11-01">
                                        <hi rend="italic">November 1, 1917</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Excellency</hi>: Referring to my recent note on
                                the subject of the participation by the Serbian Government in the
                                conference of the Allies at Paris, I have the honor to inform you
                                that the American Minister at Jassy has advised this Department that
                                the Government of Roumania likewise claims that it should
                                participate in the same conference.</p>
                            <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>